---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Kalta — Home emergency stock tracker"
  description="Track emergency supplies in real boxes with QR labels. Private, offline-first iOS app built for people who actually rotate their stock."
  schemaType="SoftwareApplication"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>Never forget what you stocked up on.</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">
            Kalta tracks every can, battery, and first-aid kit in real boxes with QR labels. It
            reminds you before anything expires, so you actually rotate your stock.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <span class="btn btn-disabled">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M17.05 20.28c-.98.95-2.05.8-3.08.35c-1.09-.46-2.09-.48-3.24 0c-1.44.62-2.2.44-3.06-.35C2.79 15.25 3.51 7.59 9.05 7.31c1.35.07 2.29.74 3.08.8c1.18-.24 2.31-.93 3.57-.84c1.51.12 2.65.72 3.4 1.8c-3.12 1.87-2.38 5.98.48 7.13c-.57 1.5-1.31 2.99-2.54 4.09zM12 7.25c-.15-2.23 1.66-4.07 3.74-4.25c.29 2.58-2.34 4.5-3.74 4.25"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Coming to App Store</span>
            </span>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#features">Learn more</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <img src="/box.png" alt="Kalta storage box illustration" class="hero-box" width="512" height="512" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="features-intro">
        <h2>A real system, for real boxes.</h2>
        <p>
          Kalta treats your emergency supplies the way a warehouse does — labeled boxes, scanned
          items, expirations, the people who maintain them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="m7.5 4.27 9 5.15"/>
              <path d="M21 8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16Z"/>
              <path d="m3.3 7 8.7 5 8.7-5"/>
              <path d="M12 22V12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>QR labels on real boxes</h3>
          <p>
            Create a warehouse, print QR labels, stick them on your boxes. Scan a label to jump
            straight to what's inside.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 5v14"/>
              <path d="M8 5v14"/>
              <path d="M12 5v14"/>
              <path d="M17 5v14"/>
              <path d="M21 5v14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Barcode-fast entry</h3>
          <p>
            Scan any EAN and Kalta pulls in the product name and category. Add an expiry date and
            you're done.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Expiry that actually warns you</h3>
          <p>
            Items are color-coded by urgency. Local reminders 30 days, 7 days, and 1 day before —
            no servers involved.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Readiness in days, not items</h3>
          <p>
            Tell Kalta who you're feeding. It turns your inventory into a number: how many days of
            food and water you actually have, against the goal you set.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1"/>
              <path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.61L23 6H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Shopping list with restock</h3>
          <p>
            Auto-suggestions from what's expired, low, or missing from your emergency kit. Check
            items off in the store; Kalta walks you through putting them back in the right box.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Share with your household</h3>
          <p>
            Invite your partner or family with a link. Everyone sees the same inventory update in
            real time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/>
              <path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/>
              <path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Works offline</h3>
          <p>
            Everything is stored locally first and synced later. Two iPhones can even sync
            directly over Bluetooth when there's no network.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Optional AI help</h3>
          <p>
            Bring your own Anthropic API key and let Claude identify products from a photo. You
            stay in control of cost and privacy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="callout">
      <h2>Zero tracking. Ever.</h2>
      <p>
        No ads, no analytics, no crash reporting, no third-party SDKs. Your data lives on your
        iPhone and is synced to an encrypted database in the EU. Only you and people you
        explicitly invite can see your inventory.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
